# Handover — Roberto feedback closeout

**Date:** 2026-05-18
**Author:** Claude Code (Opus 4.7)
**For:** Alfred / next operator
**Branch:** `fix/roberto-feedback-phase0` (pushed to `origin`, **33 commits ahead of `main`, NOT merged**)

