     1	# Roberto Scrigna Platform — Production Readiness Assessment
     2	
     3	**Date:** 2026-04-27 (supersedes 2026-03-30 assessment)
     4	**Verdict:** READY FOR DEPLOYMENT — pending runtime verification on Vercel.
     5	
     6	---
     7	
     8	## Build Verification
     9	
    10	| Check | Status | Evidence |
    11	|-------|--------|---------|
    12	| TypeScript | **Green** | `tsc --noEmit` — 0 errors across 123 source files |
    13	| Vitest | **Green** | 13 test files, 320 tests, 320 passed, 0 failures |
    14	| Production build | **Green** | `bun run build` — 24 routes compiled, 0 errors |
    15	| Fidelity fixtures | **Green** | Marco Bellini, Niccolo, Raphael — all macro targets verified |
