    18	
    19	## What Changed Since March 30
    20	
    21	The March 30 assessment declared "PRODUCTION READY" but was incomplete. A 6-agent audit
    22	on April 27 found 25 defects including security vulnerabilities, broken data paths, and
    23	mock data in production pages. A subsequent GPT-5.5 Codex sweep scored the codebase
    24	58/100 and found additional integration faults.
    25	
    26	All CRITICAL and HIGH findings were resolved across 3 commits (57 files, +7,545/-348 lines).
    27	
