    29	
    30	| Hash | Description | Files |
    31	|------|-------------|-------|
    32	| `f62c180` | Complete v1 build — client system, portal, dashboard, hardening | 53 |
    33	| `37247c4` | Fix 3 critical E2E failures + deployment guide | 5 |
    34	| `62c8dde` | Resolve Codex 58/100 findings — security, MOCK data, Inngest, intake | 9 |
    35	
    36	---
    37	
