    46	| Client list | **Green** | Search, status filter tabs, pagination (25/page), mobile card layout |
    47	| Client detail | **Green** | 4 tabs: overview (weight trend), snapshot history, plans, check-ins |
    48	| Client edit | **Green** | Profile update + new measurement with snapshot creation |
    49	| Intake form (7 pages) | **Green** | Weight, height, occupational level, skinfolds all flow to snapshot |
    50	| Plan generation | **Green** | Engine pipeline: BMR → TDEE → macros → meal plan → supplements → narrative |
    51	| Plan review (6 tabs) | **Green** | Meal ingredients with gram amounts, Italian slot labels, supplement editing |
    52	| Plan sharing | **Green** | Email share via Resend with macro summary, draft guard |
    53	| Invoice management | **Green** | CRUD, status state machine, auto-numbering, PDF download |
