    56	- **#4 Food rounding** — `engine/meal-plan/rounding.ts`: solids 5 g (≥20 g) / 1 g (<20 g); never zero for positive input.
    57	- **#10 Taxonomy** — `src/engine/sport-taxonomy.ts` (53 Appendix-D entries) + `LEGACY_DISPLAY_TO_CANONICAL` map; strength MET capped at 3 regardless of RPE. Responsive-grid pass on dashboard pages.
