    61	
    62	- `src/engine/goal-rate.ts`: `computeGoalRate({currentKg,targetKg,weeks,tdeeKcal,leanMassKg})` → required kg/wk, % BW/wk, daily deficit, band (`comfortable|moderate|aggressive|extreme`), kcal floor = `max(22×leanMassKg, 1200)`, `belowFloor`, `suggestedWeeks`. Caps: 1.0 %/wk fat-loss, 0.5 %/wk muscle-gain; band bumps up if deficit > 25 % TDEE. 17 tests.
    63	- Engine `PlanOptions.dailyDeficitKcal` subtracts from TDEE pre-macros.
    64	- `plan.estimateForClient` query (weight, lean mass, avg TDEE, saved-goal blob, weekSchedule, intake sessions — for prefill).
    65	- `/plans/generate` *Obiettivo & deficit* card: goal/target-kg/target-date, live 5-stat readout, band badge, kcal-floor block on the generate button, suggested-weeks hint, manual deficit slider + reset.
