    78	- `plan.generate` + `plan.previewWeek` accept `macroOverrides` (Zod: P 0–800 g, F 0–400 g, C 0–1500 g per day-type).
    79	- *Macro per giorno (opzionale)* card: rows only for day-types in the current schedule, engine-computed values as placeholders, per-row reset.
