    12	-- APPLY STANDALONE (Supabase SQL Editor or psql), NOT via the dev db:migrate
    13	-- runner. Fully idempotent. Re-running is a no-op.
    14	--
    15	-- IMMUTABILITY: once status='signed', a BEFORE UPDATE trigger blocks ALL further
    16	-- changes (mirrors the legal_document_version freeze pattern from 009).
    17	
    18	-- ── signature_request (shared by both tiers) ─────────────────────────────────
