    60	## 5. Architecture cheat-sheet (load-bearing facts)
    61	
    62	- **No-migration data carriers (features ride these JSONB columns):**
    63	  - Plan generation inputs (`macroOverrides`, `sourcePins`, `injuryStress`, `periodizationMode`) ride `plan.daily_targets.macro_payload`; the serialized plan bundle (`SerializedPlanResult`: `reportData.dayTypePlans[]`, `weeklyPlan`, `supplements`, `guidance`…) rides `plan.daily_targets.plan_bundle`.
    64	  - Intake extras (training_sessions w/ startTime/endTime, lifestyle, goal) ride `client_snapshot.skinfold_data._intake`.
    65	- **Storage (progress photos / training screenshots):** bucket `client-media`.
    66	  - Coach photos: `client-photos/<partner_id>/<client_id>/<uuid>-<file>`
    67	  - Training screenshots: `training-screenshots/<partner_id>/<client_id>/<uuid>-<file>`
    68	  - `(storage.foldername(name))[1]`=subtree, `[2]`=partner_id, `[3]`=client_id.
    69	  - **Migration 003** grants clients write to `training-screenshots`; **migration 007** (NOW APPLIED on prod) grants clients write to `client-photos`. Patients upload via their own JWT (`createSupabaseBrowser()`), RLS-scoped to their folder.
    70	- **Testing (vitest env = "node", no jsdom/RTL):**
    71	  - Render components with `renderToStaticMarkup` (react-dom/server) + `createElement`; assert on the HTML string. Effects DON'T run in SSR — so keep `createSupabaseBrowser()`/tRPC hooks OUT of render paths (use dynamic `import()` inside handlers/effects).
    72	  - Test logic as **pure exported helpers** with injectable deps (mock with `vi.fn`). `noUncheckedIndexedAccess` is ON → guard `arr[0]?.x` and use named consts, not `arr[0].x`.
    73	  - Mocked-caller router tests: `vi.mock("server-only")` + `vi.mock("next/headers")` + chainable fake supabase + `router.createCaller({…} as never)`; UUID inputs need valid UUID constants.
    74	- **`<img>` convention:** prefer next/image, but `<img>` is allowed with `// eslint-disable-next-line @next/next/no-img-element` (it's a warning, not a build error).
    75	- **tRPC `useUtils()` gotcha:** the utils proxy collides with the `client` router name → `utils.portal.x` fails to typecheck. Use `someQuery.refetch()` instead of `utils.*.invalidate()`.
    76	- **Plan review page** (`src/app/(dashboard)/plans/[id]/review/page.tsx`, ~1900 lines) already owns `createVersionMutation` (#24 regenerate flow) + `buildCreateVersionInput(planId, reason)` — reuse these for any "regenerate" affordance.
