  ✓ Audit dimensions 1–7 with line-level evidence
  ✓ Audit dimensions 8–14, including RLS, contracts, and test gaps
  → Verify every proposed citation and evidence tier
  • Write and acceptance-check docs/polish/lanes/CODE-AUDIT-CODEX.md
